sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as React frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant Security as Lexik JWT
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    User->>Frontend: Submit email and password
    Frontend->>API: POST /api/login_check
    API->>DB: Load user by email
    DB-->>API: User record + hashed password
    API->>Security: Validate credentials and build JWT
    Security-->>API: Signed token
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + token
    Frontend-->>User: Store token and open dashboard
